steps.title: Use another method

footer.get_help_text: Don't have any of these? Get help

test_cases.test_case: TC001 - Positive flow for email login
test_cases.objective: To verify the successful sign in using email and password
test_steps: Enter valid email address and password
Check if user is redirected to dashboard page
expected_results: User should be able to log in successfully
User should be redirected to dashboard page after successful login

test_cases.test_case: TC002 - Negative flow for email login with invalid email
test_cases.objective: To verify the error message when user enters an invalid email
test_steps: Enter an invalid email and password
Check if user is not redirected to dashboard page
expected_results: User should see an error message for invalid email
User should not be redirected to dashboard page

test_cases.test_case: TC003 - Negative flow for email login with incorrect password
test_cases.objective: To verify the error message when user enters an incorrect password
test_steps: Enter a valid email and an incorrect password
Check if user is not redirected to dashboard page
expected_results: User should see an error message for incorrect password
User should not be redirected to dashboard page

test_cases.test_case: TC004 - Edge case flow for email login with email address in boundary values
test_cases.objective: To verify the successful sign in when user enters an email address in boundary values
test_steps: Enter a valid email address in boundary values and password
Check if user is redirected to dashboard page
expected_results: User should be able to log in successfully
User should be redirected to dashboard page after successful login

test_cases.test_case: TC005 - Alternate flow for social login using Apple
test_cases.objective: To verify the successful sign in using social login with Apple
test_steps: Click on social login option for Apple
Follow the prompts to allow access to Scoreboard
Check if user is redirected to dashboard page
expected_results: User should be able to log in successfully using Apple
User should be redirected to dashboard page after successful login

test_cases.test_case: TC006 - Negative flow for social login with Apple
test_cases.objective: To verify the error message when user cancels the social login prompt
test_steps: Click on social login option for Apple
Click on cancel button in the prompt
Check if user is not redirected to dashboard page
expected_results: User should see an error message when cancels the prompt
User should not be redirected to dashboard page

test_cases.objective: To verify the successful sign in when user enters an email address in boundary values
test_steps: Click on social login option for Apple
Follow the prompts to allow access to Scoreboard
Check if user is redirected to dashboard page
expected_results: User should be able to log in successfully using Apple
User should be redirected to dashboard page after successful login
